              <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A marketing funnel spans awareness through advocacy. A sales funnel focuses on opportunity through close. Marketing feeds the sales funnel — when marketing hands off a qualified lead, the sales funnel takes over. They are sequential, not competing frameworks.</p></div></div>
